{
  "style": "",
  "texts": [
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) technologies are rapidly advancing, enhancing human capabilities across various fields spanning from finance to medicine.",
    "Despite their numerous advantages, AI systems can exhibit biased judgements in domains ranging from perception to emotion.",
    "Here, in a series of experiments (n = 1,401 participants), we reveal a feedback loop where human-AI interactions alter processes underlying human perceptual, emotional and social judgements, subsequently amplifying biases in humans.",
    "This amplification is significantly greater than that observed in interactions between humans, due to both the tendency of AI systems to amplify biases and the way humans perceive AI systems.",
    "Participants are often unaware of the extent of the AI's influence, rendering them more susceptible to it."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}